    "notes": [
      "This config follows the MX2 flexible-format mapping described in the local Omron option-board manuals.",
      "The mapped exchange uses Modbus coils 0000h through 000Fh for control, coils 0010h through 001Fh for status, registers 0001h and 0002h for frequency reference, and registers 1001h and 1002h for output-frequency monitoring.",
      "The configured listen address and unit ID are simulator choices rather than Omron-documented defaults.",
      "The configured port falls back to Modbus TCP default 502 because no Omron-specific port override was verified.",
      "No Omron-specific runtime behavior is implemented in Go yet."
    ]
  },
